overview: 18 strangers move into a majestic mansion to complete group missions to win silver bars for their shared prize pool, which could reach up to $100,000. However, some of them are traitors who will try to manipulate the group and kill a faithful person every evening in order to be the only ones to get their hands on the loot. In an exhilarating reality show where lying rhymes with victory, will the traitors be unmasked in time by the faithful?
